import React from 'react';
import { 
  Grid, 
  Paper, 
  Typography, 
  Box, 
  Card, 
  CardContent, 
  CardHeader, 
  Button
} from '@mui/material';
import ShoppingCartIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ShoppingCart';
import InventoryIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Inventory';
import StoreIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Store';
import PeopleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/People';

const Dashboard = () => {
  return (
    <Box>
      <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom>
        Dashboard
      </Typography>
      
      <Grid container spacing={3} mb={4}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Paper
            sx={{
              p: 2,
              display: 'flex',
              flexDirection: 'column',
              height: 140,
              bgcolor: 'primary.light',
              color: 'white'
            }}
          >
            <Typography component="h2" variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Ventas Totales
            </Typography>
            <Typography component="p" variant="h4">
              $24,300
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 'auto', opacity: 0.7 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2">
                Últimos 30 días
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Paper
            sx={{
              p: 2,
              display: 'flex',
              flexDirection: 'column',
              height: 140,
              bgcolor: 'success.light',
              color: 'white'
            }}
          >
            <Typography component="h2" variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Inventario
            </Typography>
            <Typography component="p" variant="h4">
              1,254
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 'auto', opacity: 0.7 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2">
                Productos en stock
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Paper
            sx={{
              p: 2,
              display: 'flex',
              flexDirection: 'column',
              height: 140,
              bgcolor: 'warning.light',
              color: 'white'
            }}
          >
            <Typography component="h2" variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Sucursales
            </Typography>
            <Typography component="p" variant="h4">
              3
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 'auto', opacity: 0.7 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2">
                Activas
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Paper
            sx={{
              p: 2,
              display: 'flex',
              flexDirection: 'column',
              height: 140,
              bgcolor: 'info.light',
              color: 'white'
            }}
          >
            <Typography component="h2" variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Empleados
            </Typography>
            <Typography component="p" variant="h4">
              15
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ mt: 'auto', opacity: 0.7 }}>
              <Typography variant="body2">
                Registrados
              </Typography>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      
      <Grid container spacing={3}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader title="Acciones Rápidas" />
            <CardContent>
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                  <Button
                    fullWidth
                    variant="contained"
                    color="primary"
                    startIcon={<ShoppingCartIcon />}
                    sx={{ py: 1 }}
                  >
                    Nueva Venta
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                  <Button
                    fullWidth
                    variant="contained"
                    color="success"
                    startIcon={<InventoryIcon />}
                    sx={{ py: 1 }}
                  >
                    Gestionar Inventario
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                  <Button
                    fullWidth
                    variant="contained"
                    color="warning"
                    startIcon={<StoreIcon />}
                    sx={{ py: 1 }}
                  >
                    Ver Sucursales
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                  <Button
                    fullWidth
                    variant="contained"
                    color="info"
                    startIcon={<PeopleIcon />}
                    sx={{ py: 1 }}
                  >
                    Administrar Usuarios
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
        
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Card>
            <CardHeader title="Productos con Bajo Stock" />
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="body1">
                No hay productos con stock bajo en este momento.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
